EXEC P_THEME_LIST(SEQ_TNO.NEXTVAL,'ADMIN','Where the past & present of fashion converge','<p><img class="main-img" src="http://english.visitseoul.net/comm/getImage?srvcId=MEDIA&amp;parentSn=26775&amp;fileTy=MEDIA&amp;fileNo=1" alt="Find the Past &amp; Present of Shopping and Fashion at the Dongdaemun Fashion Cluster" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 1000px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 17px;"></p><p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><p class="" style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">Dongdaemun Fashion Cluster is the mecca of K-fashion. It is a must-visit area for foreign tourists. Its popularity is on the rise due to the surging Korean Wave. In addition to shopping for clothing, the area captivates visitors through its renowned tourist attractions like Cheonggyecheon Stream and Dongdaemun Design Plaza.</p><p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><p style="padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: center; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;"><img src="http://english.visitseoul.net/comm/getImage?srvcId=MEDIA&amp;parentSn=26783&amp;fileTy=MEDIA&amp;fileNo=1" alt="1" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;"></p><h3 class="one" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.375em; color: rgb(63, 109, 158); text-align: center; width: 1000px; line-height: 1.3; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">Traditional meets modern</h3><h5 style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 20px; font-size: 32px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: center; width: 1000px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">Dongdaemun Fashion Cluster</h5><p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><p><img class