ans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><p><img class="main-img" src="http://english.visitseoul.net/comm/getImage?srvcId=MEDIA&amp;parentSn=26780&amp;fileTy=MEDIA&amp;fileNo=1" alt="Migliore" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 1000px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 17px;"></p><p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><p class="" style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">Migliore and Doota Mall are the flagship shopping malls of the Dongdaemun Fashion Cluster. Migliore is a 11-story mega shopping mall. Its lower floors are devoted to a wide range of clothing items, from casual to formal wear, while the fifth floor and up specialize in bags, footwear, and household goods. Doota Mall features global brands as well as local brands. The fourth floor is devoted to K-beauty products. If you’re interested in Korean skin-care products, you can expect to be hauling high-quality K-beauty goods from the shopping mall with both hands.</p><p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 1000px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Nanum Barun Gothic&quot;, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;">&nbsp;</p><div class="cnt-blockquote" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 30px; background: rgb(245, 245, 245); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: auto; font-family: 